        "id": "28f5803a-9436-4798-a288-332ac18a6bbf",
        "type": "paragraph",
        "text": "Impact investments occur across asset classes and investment amounts. Among the best-known mechanism is private equity or venture capital. \"[[Social venture capital]]\", or \"patient capital\", impact investments are structured similarly to those in the rest of the venture capital community. Investors may take an active role mentoring or leading the growth of the company,[http://www.nasdaq.com/article/wealthy-attracted-to-impact-investing-cm23388 Wealthy Attracted To Impact Investing] similar to the way a venture capital firm assists in the growth of an early-stage company. Hedge funds and private equity funds may also pursue impact investing strategies."
